						<div class="postbody">Yes; that's something I exploited for making samples with a looped part: load $4012 and $4013 with begin and length of sample, restart playback with loop on, load immediatly $4012 and $4013 with start and length of loop point. When the first part is played the loop part goes on. Tested on a NES with a Powerpak and it works reliably.</div>

